<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,354,438,463]" pageId="8" pageNumber="229">Distribution:</emphasis>
Galápagos.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="229" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1436,294,571]" pageId="8" pageNumber="229">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,317,474,499]" pageId="8" pageNumber="229">Remarks:</emphasis>
This species shows a broad ecological spectrum and can inhabit different microhabitats in the littoral area, from rocky shore and mangrove litter to dryer habitats above the intertidal zone (Pfingstl &amp; Schatz 2017).
</paragraph>
